{"tid":2360663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞馬遜指不再為受保守派歡迎的社交平台程式Parler提供雲端服務","createTime":"2021-01-10T03:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T16:12:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c427c922688745bcd5479c353f34b47e61617ba2","tid":2360663,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"亞馬遜指不再為社交平台程式Parler提供雲端服務<br />\n<br />\n美國電子商務企業亞馬遜表示，不再為社交平台程式「Parler」提供雲端服務，指「Parler」未能對未能充分應對平台上的暴力威脅帖文。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle及蘋果公司亦宣布把「Parler」從應用程式商店下架，表示「Parler」未能對平台上的發言作出足夠監管，出現過多鼓勵暴力和犯罪的帖文。蘋果表示支持不同觀點，但「Parler」沒採取足夠措施，應對為民眾安全造成的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n「Parler」深受保守派歡迎。近日，因為Twitter同Facebook打擊散播錯誤訊息和煽動暴力的帖文，大批特朗普支持者轉用「Parler」。截至當地周六早上，「Parler」遭蘋果下架前，於平台的免費軟件列表中排第一。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2374141&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=48810f03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374141</a>"},{"pid":"6fc3cdd31289133e2d3082f4fd8bd671fb1ee2c0","tid":2360663,"uid":35924,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"呢d 時候憲法第一修正案應該要做野啦"},{"pid":"dc473d69a0a15a6c58dbf526479b64e3ad28d2e8","tid":2360663,"uid":60545,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"啲企業真係「好民主」 就嚟取代埋美國聯邦政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7823ab1bcc32724ab15b43cce6a20c7b0f13d02d","tid":2360663,"uid":92448,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"looting is peaceful<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fe779e7e37e0a2fdad8f904f027ba68e0e2d1b","tid":2360663,"uid":191926,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"全面it civil war <br />\n邊個禁  邊個出走<br />\n股價自然跌<img 